      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "TESTING TABLES"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In the normal course of dialog development, tables are created,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "modified and and displayed in panels. To display or alter a table,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "select Dialog Test Option 3."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Table Test presents a select list of all disk-based tables. Tables"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "which are created with the NOWRITE option are not displayed in the select list."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "With Table Test you can:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  Edit a table using the 'E' line command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  Copy the table using the 'C' line command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  Delete the table using the 'D' line command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  Rename the table using the 'R' line command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
